GSD.description:
mmc: sdio: fix possible resource leaks in some error paths

This is an automated ID intended to aid in discovery of potential security vulnerabilities. The actual impact and attack plausibility have not yet been proven.
This ID is fixed in Linux Kernel version v4.19.273 by commit 5c7858adada31dbed042448cff6997dd6efc472a, it was introduced in version v2.6.33 by commit 3d10a1ba0d37c8f5fd5afcdda00613fbb8a90bf5. For more details please see the references link.
